[i]Beast Fang[/i] – Whenever equipped creature attacks, reveal the top card of your library until you reveal a creature card. Put that card onto the battlefield tapped and attacking. Put the rest of the revealed cards on the bottom of your library in any order.
[i]Storm Dragon Sign[/i] – {2}, Exile Blutgang: The next creature spell you cast this turn has storm. The “legend rule” doesn't apply to creatures you control for the rest of the game. Activate only if equipped creature attacked this turn.
